        name: String,
    },
    /// A global import which may have a number of vendor prefixes associated
    /// with it, like `webkitAudioPrefix`. The `name` is the name to test
    /// whether it's prefixed.
    VendorPrefixed { name: String, prefixes: Vec<String> },
